{"tid":997224,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[你們的女神] 36歳文凱玲住劏房4年 停工入院做子宮手術：有錢先敢入行","createTime":"2019-01-27T03:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T07:35:53.000Z","uid":12558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5b3293edf6d8a20f6303addfb6fbb11d09310dde","tid":997224,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T03:55:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20190127/2_651077_0/-%E8%8D%B7%E9%87%8C%E6%B4%BB%E6%98%8E%E7%8F%A0%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B%E6%A5%AD%E7%B7%9A-%E6%96%87%E5%87%B1%E7%8E%B2%E4%BD%8F%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF4%E5%B9%B4-%E5%81%9C%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%A5%E9%99%A2%E5%81%9A%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93-%E6%9C%89%E9%8C%A2%E5%85%88%E6%95%A2%E5%85%A5%E8%A1%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190127%2F2_651077_0%2F-%25E8%258D%25B7%25E9%2587%258C%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E6%2598%258E%25E7%258F%25A0%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%2587%25B1%25E7%258E%25B2%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%258A%258F%25E6%2588%25BF4%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E5%2581%259C%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%2581%259A%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25A1%2593-%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%258C%25A2%25E5%2585%2588%25E6%2595%25A2%25E5%2585%25A5%25E8%25A1%258C&d=S7XkTtUUaO0bij%2BLmYwwlJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=5e2be935\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190127%2F2_651077_0%2F-%25E8%258D%25B7%25E9%2587%258C%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E6%2598%258E%25E7%258F%25A0%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%2587%25B1%25E7%258E%25B2%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%258A%258F%25E6%2588%25BF4%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E5%2581%259C%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%2581%259A%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25A1%2593-%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%258C%25A2%25E5%2585%2588%25E6%2595%25A2%25E5%2585%25A5%25E8%25A1%258C&h=13be03df\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20190127/2_651077_0/-%E8%8D%B7%E9%87%8C%E6%B4%BB%E6%98%8E%E7%8F%A0%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B%E6%A5%AD%E7%B7%9A-%E6%96%87%E5%87%B1%E7%8E%B2%E4%BD%8F%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF4%E5%B9%B4-%E5%81%9C%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%A5%E9%99%A2%E5%81%9A%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93-%E6%9C%89%E9%8C%A2%E5%85%88%E6%95%A2%E5%85%A5%E8%A1%8C</a><br />\n<br />\n正在熱播的電視劇《荷里活有個大老千》，劇中的明珠努力工作，希望找到機會拍電影成為女主角。現實的文凱玲，是10年落選港姐，喜歡電影的她，比賽後卻未有全身投入娛樂圈，反而繼續做空姐，遇到有拍戲機會，她才向公司請假。原來有四年時間，她更一直租住百呎劏房，為的是可以儲夠彈藥，才敢正式入娛樂圈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港大學心理學系畢業的文凱玲</span>，大學時期已經替學生補習交學費，到出來工作，更負責家裡大部分開支。要入娛樂圈，她明知收入不穩定，所以一直未有放棄空姐工作，在衣食住行更慳住用，她曾經跟朋友說要儲夠錢先敢入行。兩年多前，她正式簽約經理人公司，接了多部電影和電視劇，才做全職演員。上年，她因切割子宮肌瘤入院做手術，因為傷口深，足足休息了幾個月，雖然沒有收入，幸好她向來生活慳儉有積蓄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文凱玲一直搏殺，在跟杜汶澤合拍電影《唐伯虎衝上雲霄》時，飾演秋香的她，已經豁出去拍出浴戲露大半球。到上年的《冒險王衛斯理之支離人》，她又將留了多年的長髮剪短扮演殺手，跟林家楝做對手戲，今次跟好戲BABY JOHN做情侶，她又成為劇中被抽水最多的女角，好有挑戰性。"},{"pid":"afcda1b4df0623436b946d5c5d071a2a5096e227","tid":997224,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:36:16.000Z","msg":"36歳,感覺演藝事業先岩岩起步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914e8b16f26f6b1526736b309512d0004ec2545e","tid":997224,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afcda1b4df0623436b946d5c5d071a2a5096e227","tid":997224,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:36:16.000Z","msg":"36歳,感覺演藝事業先岩岩起步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:37:26.000Z","msg":"要紅既 好似ali 咁m2,3年已經夠"},{"pid":"3269609766a30f2a543f31a42b25026d5c8c1a8a","tid":997224,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:37:49.000Z","msg":"佢好正<br />\n好想佢閪我面"},{"pid":"7179ad2e57ff584197db8069ea13817b3320d65d","tid":997224,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:38:20.000Z","msg":"老g"},{"pid":"fd003708bacdc379595db66bb9c6f5821b7